{"title":"Earthquake - Title","type":"markdown","params":{"markdown":"# World's Earthquakes

### Hot Areas

- [Japan](/app/kibana#/dashboard/Earthquake-Japan)
- [Indonesia](/app/kibana#/dashboard/Earthquake-Indonesia)
- [Himalayas](/app/kibana#/dashboard/Earthquake-Himalayas)
- [Mediterranean Region](/app/kibana#/dashboard/Earthquake-Mediterranean-Region)
- [West Coast, USA](/app/kibana#/dashboard/Earthquake-West-Coast)

### Historical Events

- [Loma Prieta, 1989](/app/kibana#/dashboard/Earthquake-Loma-Prieta) ([Wikipedia](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/1989_Loma_Prieta_earthquake))
- [zmit, 1999](/app/kibana#/dashboard/Earthquake-Izmit) ([Wikipedia](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/1999_zmit_earthquake))
- [Sumatra, 2004, 2005](/app/kibana#/dashboard/Earthquake-Sumatra) ([Wikipedia](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2004_Indian_Ocean_earthquake_and_tsunami))
- [Haiti, 2010](/app/kibana#/dashboard/Earthquake-Haiti) ([Wikipedia](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2010_Haiti_earthquake))
- [Tohoku, 2011](/app/kibana#/dashboard/Earthquake-Tohoku) ([Wikipedia](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2011_Thoku_earthquake_and_tsunami))

### Quarries and Nuclear Blasts

- [Refinery Explosion at Texas, USA, 2008](/app/kibana#/dashboard/Earthquake-Blast-Big-Spring) ([NBC News](http://www.nbcnews.com/id/23222087/ns/us_news-life/t/injured-explosion-texas-refinery/#.V3WR41dQyoE))
- [Nevada, USA](/app/kibana#/dashboard/Earthquake-Blast-Nevada)
- [D.P.R. Korea](/app/kibana#/dashboard/Earthquake-Blast-DPRK)

###  

Go back to [the world map](/app/kibana#/dashboard/Earthquake) or compare with [the world population density and nuclear plant locations](/app/kibana#/dashboard/Earthquake-vs-Population-slash-Nuclear-Plants).
